<div class="sharethis-inline-share-buttons" data-title="The crash of the anvil at the nightclub school: Sheila Rock&#8217;s New Romantics" data-url="https://dangerousminds.net/comments/the_crash_of_the_anvil_at_the_nightclub_school_sheila_rocks_new_romant" data-username="DangerMindsBlog"></div>
