<div class="sharethis-inline-share-buttons" data-title="Kenneth Anger RIP: The Magus of American Cinema dead at 96" data-url="https://dangerousminds.net/comments/kenneth_anger_rip_the_magus_of_american_cinema_dead_at_96" data-username="DangerMindsBlog"></div>
